  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/5e82a83f68188ce94c464d750ff411aa.avif?t=1723477565\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br>\"7 Meters Away. Oscar and the Cell of the Soul\" is a point-and-click game where you assume the role of Óscar, a young package deliveryman. After what was supposed to be his last delivery of the day, Oscar finds himself trapped in a cell whose origin is lost in the shadows of the past.<br><br>Use your environment and transform objects into tools to progress in the story; each object is a piece of the puzzle that will lead him to discover the hidden truth behind The Cell of the Soul.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/4a9a251c49c011ee72fb93d15676e7ea.poster.avif?t=1723477565\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/4a9a251c49c011ee72fb93d15676e7ea.webm?t=1723477565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/4a9a251c49c011ee72fb93d15676e7ea.mp4?t=1723477565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pixel Art.</h2>A blend of retro finishes from classic titles with modern lighting techniques.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Verb Coin:</strong></h2> Four action verbs ( look, take, use and speak) in the classic verb coin that add dynamism to the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong></h2> The estimated time to complete the game for experienced players is 1 to 2 hours for the average player.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/195d46ceba9dd4cd3458f39af4cfe330.avif?t=1723477565\" width=616 height=107 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/5e82a83f68188ce94c464d750ff411aa.avif?t=1723477565\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br>\"7 Meters Away. Oscar and the Cell of the Soul\" is a point-and-click game where you assume the role of Óscar, a young package deliveryman. After what was supposed to be his last delivery of the day, Oscar finds himself trapped in a cell whose origin is lost in the shadows of the past.<br><br>Use your environment and transform objects into tools to progress in the story; each object is a piece of the puzzle that will lead him to discover the hidden truth behind The Cell of the Soul.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/4a9a251c49c011ee72fb93d15676e7ea.poster.avif?t=1723477565\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/4a9a251c49c011ee72fb93d15676e7ea.webm?t=1723477565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/4a9a251c49c011ee72fb93d15676e7ea.mp4?t=1723477565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pixel Art.</h2>A blend of retro finishes from classic titles with modern lighting techniques.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Verb Coin:</strong></h2> Four action verbs ( look, take, use and speak) in the classic verb coin that add dynamism to the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong></h2> The estimated time to complete the game for experienced players is 1 to 2 hours for the average player.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018480/extras/195d46ceba9dd4cd3458f39af4cfe330.avif?t=1723477565\" width=616 height=107 /></span>",
